<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <link href="data:image/png;base64," rel="icon">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rental Mobil - Contact</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
            font-size: 10px;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: -20px 0 50px;
            padding: 10px;
            background-image: url('https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQpJBVp3KBjlqMJ1RLFnrwsir4-pKRP8QgMVg&s');
        }

        .container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 14px 28px aquamarine, 0 10px 10px blue;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 768px;
            max-width: 100%;
            min-height: 522px;
            min-width: 370px;
        }

        .card-container {
            display: flex;
        }

        .left {
            flex: 1;
            height: 522px;
            background-color: #00b4cf;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .left-container {
            width: 80%;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 22px;
        }

        .left p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .bold-text {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .right {
            display: flex;
            flex: 1;
            height: 460px;
            background-color: white;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .right-container {
            width: 70%;
            height: 80%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        input,
        textarea {
            background-color: aliceblue;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            margin: 8px 0;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        input:focus, textarea:focus {
            outline: 1px solid #00b4cf;
        }

        button {
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #00b4cf;
            background-color: #00b4cf;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 12px 45px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: transform 80ms ease-out;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button:hover {
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        textarea {
            height: 100px;
        }

        .back-button {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ffffff;
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 12px 45px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: transform 80ms ease-out;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .back-button:hover {
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        /* responsive */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px){
            .left {
                display: none;
            }

            .lg-view {
                display: none;
            }
        }

        @media only screen and (min-width: 600px) {
            .sm-view {
                display: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card-container">
            <div class="left">
                <div class="left-container">
                    <p>Jika ada permasalahan di wabsite segera hubungi kami dengan pesan anda melalui halaman ini, kami berharap anda senang dan puas dengan persediaan yang ada di web site kami.</p>
                    <br>
                    <p class="bold-text">Jangan lupa terus rental mobil di RentalYuk :]</p>
                    <button class="back-button" onclick="history.back()">Kembali</button>
                </div>  
            </div>
            <div class="right">
                <div class="right-container">
                    <form action="">
                        <h2 class="lg-view">Hubungi Kami</h2>
                        <h2 class="sm-view">Hubungi Kami</h2>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Nama">
                        <input type="email" placeholder="Alamat Email">
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Perusahaan">
                        <input type="phone" placeholder="Telepon">
                        <textarea rows="10" placeholder="Pesan"></textarea>
                        <button>Kirim</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>     
    </div>
</body>
</html>
